data.title: Love their turkey tacos
data.text: I eat at Del Taco because they are so close to my home and so very, very convenient. Love their inferno sauce and I always order the same thing: Turkey tacos, crispy shell, no cheese. They always fill up the shell with veggies in the place of the cheese, which I love. Their fries are also very good.

data.title: Absolutely the worst customer service ...
data.text:
The food is actually pretty good... depending on the day...and If you get what you order...
The problem?.. you rarely get what you order. 
 Absolutely the slowest service in town.  By far. I was a regular 2 or 3 times a week customer 2 yrs ago... it has deteriorated in service and food standards so badly that I may stop in once every couple months... and still, I'm disappointed.  
Tonight we got 3 meals...2 were wrong. 
We are done.

data.title: Quick food, drive-thru convenient!
data.text: Quick food, inexpensive.  Not authentic Mexican, but some tasty items on the menu.  The turkey tacos are a great addition to the menu, healthier.  Good place to stop in or drive thru if you want cheap eats. Service is quick and staff is pleasant.  Open lunch, dinnertime and late evening.  Convenient hours and indoor or outdoor seating available.

data.title: Not up to the Del Taco standards
data.text:
I have eating at this restaurant before and it always been pretty good for fast food Mexican food. We had is to go my wife hade the taco salad and she said it was very good. I had my usual  a combination burrito and a Beef burrito. Both burrito's were not good. the tortilla shells were old and the beef  was old and tasted burnt.  We were there at 7:35 PM. so I guess you don't go late.

I will probably go back but not at night.

data.title: In a Hurry for a Quick Bite
data.text: We liked the food the first several visits and then it seemed not all that great. If you're in a hurry, it makes for a quick meal.

data.title: I seem to eat here more than I should.
data.text: I live a few blocks from a relatively new Del Taco. It seems that whenever I've got a project going or am too busy to cook I'll go there as often as anywhere else. The tacos at this particular establishment are always made to order. The fries are always nice and fresh and hot, and the place is well kept. That's about the best you can ask for of a fast food establishment. This is a good one, if you like Del Taco.
